You deserve to go and get that workout done but yes, I know the leakage problem always makes us take a step back. 😚
But not anymore, because I came across Evereve’s period panty to protect you from all sides when you are bleeding heavily. An ultimate product to protect you on your tough days and another product, drum rolls please, is Evereve’s sanitary napkins with soft cushions and spacious protection for the days you are not bleeding so heavily and can go get your tasks done normally. I am literally in love with this combo and I think it is a savior for every woman who faces period hurdles. I stan these products, they have changed my life and I think you should get your hands on it for a happier period experience. Now you do not have to worry about “that time of the month”. Happy and adventurous periods y’all!
